<body>
        <!-- LANDING JUMBOTRON -->
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <h1 class="logo">Stemma</h1>
                <h2>
                    Capturing the moments, people, places, and everything in between that makes your life special is made easy with Stemma.
                </h2>
                <div class="cta">
                    <a class="btn btn-success" href="~/Views/Account/Register.cshtml"> <i class="fa fa-envira" style="font-size: 15px"></i>Get started</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- LANDING INTROS -->
        <div class="container" id="landing-page-text-boxes">
            <div class="box col-md-3">
                <div class="textbox">
                    <h2>The little things...</h2>
                    <p>
                        How do you capture life's little everyday moments?
                        Do you need reminded to take a picture with a friend or family member?
                        Do you want to record a story or a song?
                        Never forget a moment with the help of Stemma.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box col-md-3">
                <div class="textbox">
                    <h2>The big things...</h2>
                    <p>Record all of those major life-changing moments - weddings, graduations, births, a new job, and buying a house - what changed in your life and what changed you. Keep track of it all with Stemma.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box col-md-3">
                <div class="textbox">
                    <h2>What came before...</h2>
                    <p>Begin to archive your family history. Upload pictures, create events, record a family history, and organize it in one place with the help of Stemma.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box col-md-3">
                <div class="textbox">
                    <h2>...and what is yet to come.</h2>
                    <p>Leave life lessons, stories, and memories for future generations. Preserve your history for your loved ones with the help of Stemma.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
